South Africa’s Head of Mineral Resources, Nogxina, to Step Down This Month

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-06-08T06:13:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/south-africa-s-head-of-mineral-resources-nogxina-to-step-down-this-month.html
The director-general of  South
Africa ’s mineral resources department, Sandile Nogxina, took
early retirement effective at the end of this month, Mineral
Resources Minister Susan Shabangu said in a speech made
yesterday and e-mailed today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
